00:38:05.941 --> 00:38:10.830
and let us see which religious organization

00:38:11.031 --> 00:38:12.621
has granted that to people.

00:38:12.861 --> 00:38:16.076
It’s only your Spirit, when It is awakened and reborn,

00:38:16.277 --> 00:38:18.340
you can have that innocence within you.

