In the Universe this is the chakra,

00:42:48.701 --> 00:42:53.039
Vishuddhi chakra, is what America represents.

00:42:53.240 --> 00:42:55.621
Because America has a responsibility,

00:42:55.861 --> 00:42:57.765
this center has the responsibility.

